                            <comment id="15402425" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 1 Aug 2016 17:06:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1754780 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1754780&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1754780&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3428&quot; title=&quot;Objects inherited from its parents are lost in PDFBox while copying&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3428&quot;&gt;PDFBOX-3428&lt;/a&gt;: remove calls that are now done in importPage&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15402430" author="tilman" created="Mon, 1 Aug 2016 17:08:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not yet sure about whether to also copy the resources... especially after looking at &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-28&quot; title=&quot;Spliiting a PDF creates unnecessarily large chunks&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-28&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-28&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and related issues. For now, I&apos;ll just added all except the setResources() call and added a warning. I&apos;ve targeted it to 2.0.4 so we don&apos;t forget to make a decision.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15712629" author="tilman" created="Thu, 1 Dec 2016 18:08:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m more undecided than ever after reading &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-28&quot; title=&quot;Spliiting a PDF creates unnecessarily large chunks&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-28&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-28&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; once again.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15714827" author="lehmi" created="Fri, 2 Dec 2016 11:10:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like some sort of analyzer is needed to determine wether the global resources are used or not.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16674361" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 4 Nov 2018 10:10:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1845720 from tilman@apache.org in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1845720&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1845720&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3428&quot; title=&quot;Objects inherited from its parents are lost in PDFBox while copying&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3428&quot;&gt;PDFBOX-3428&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3280&quot; title=&quot;PDDocument.importPage does not deep clone source page&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3280&quot;&gt;PDFBOX-3280&lt;/a&gt;: format + improve + correct javadoc&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16674363" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 4 Nov 2018 10:10:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1845721 from tilman@apache.org in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1845721&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1845721&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3428&quot; title=&quot;Objects inherited from its parents are lost in PDFBox while copying&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3428&quot;&gt;PDFBOX-3428&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3280&quot; title=&quot;PDDocument.importPage does not deep clone source page&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3280&quot;&gt;PDFBOX-3280&lt;/a&gt;: format + improve + correct javadoc&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16674367" author="tilman" created="Sun, 4 Nov 2018 10:13:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Code to analyze the page content stream to find out what is really used would need some time to be written. (And I think that in some cases (type 3 fonts?) objects deep down want access to the page resources, if true then it is even more tricky)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My current thought is to make it configurable through an boolean extra parameter or through an extra method.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
